These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
Game: canasta, domino, mah-jongg, chess
1. Game:chess is on the left or right of Game:canasta##3
2. Game:canasta is somewhere to the right of Game:chess##5
3. Game:domino is not to the left of Game:mah-jongg##8
4. Game:domino is on the left of Game:chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | domino | chess | canasta |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
Pet: horse, lizard, cat, pony
1. Pet:horse is not to the right of Pet:pony##8
2. Pet:lizard is between Pet:pony and Pet:cat##2
3. Pet:lizard is on the left of Pet:pony##1
4. Pet:pony is somewhere to the right of Pet:horse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| Pet   | horse | cat | lizard | pony |

 #################################
 
